## Build

```
cd demo-src/apps/web && npm run build   # 30 static pages, 0 type errors, 0 lint warnings
cp -r out/. ../../../michaelwegter.com/public/demos/trucking-freight-factoring-and-banking/
```

Committed and pushed to `michaelwegter.com` main (`2fd6d80`). GH Pages auto-deploy triggered.

