## Human action (optional, not required for demo)

If you want the real NestJS backend to respond (real DB):
1. Provision Neon Postgres, set `DATABASE_URL` + `JWT_SECRET` in environment.
2. `pnpm --filter @factoring/api run seed` (seeds 3 users, 4 accounts, 5 invoices).
3. Start NestJS: `node demo-src/apps/api/dist/apps/api/src/main.js`.
4. Restart Flask so `factoring_gateway_blueprint` is loaded.
5. When real API responds, mock mode is never activated and all ops hit the real DB.

